! Title: Flixbaba + Lanky-Bar Blocklist
! Description: Blocks lanky-bar.com and related scripts/popups on flixbaba.tv
! Last updated: 2025-08-20
! Homepage: https://github.com/YOURUSERNAME/adguard-filters

! Block all requests to lanky-bar.com (ads, popups, redirects)
||lanky-bar.com^

! Block any lanky-bar scripts loaded from flixbaba.tv
flixbaba.tv##^script:has-text(lanky-bar)

! Block hidden elements that trigger lanky-bar on clicks
flixbaba.tv##a[href*="lanky-bar"]
flixbaba.tv##a:has-text(lanky-bar)
flixbaba.tv##div:has(a[href*="lanky-bar"])

! Block inline JavaScript containing lanky-bar references
/.*lanky-bar\.com.*/$script,domain=flixbaba.tv
